Davenport.Moline Township, Rock Island County, Ill:
Moline Township is located in Rock Island County, Illinois, USA. At the 2010 census, its population was 23,529 and it contained 10,314 housing units.


== Geography ==
According to the 2010 census, the township has a total area of 7.71 square miles (20.0 km2), of which 6.44 square miles (16.7 km2) (or 83.53%) is land and 1.27 square miles (3.3 km2) (or 16.47%) is water.
